Package com.i2group.apollo.model.security.dynamic.transport

Contains classes for communicating information about the contents of a dynamic security schema to other parts of an i2 Analyze deployment.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Dimension
    A dimension for security permissions in the security schema.
    DimensionValue
    A possible value for a Dimension.
    GroupPermissions
    The Collection of Permissions for a user group.
    Groups
    The collection of GroupPermissions.
    Permission
    A specification of the security access or grant level that is associated with a particular dimension value in a dynamic security schema.
    Permissions
    A collection of Permissions that are associated with a particular dimension in a dynamic security schema.
    SecurityDimensions
    The security access and grant security Dimensions.
    SecuritySchema
    The security schema.
